 "remarks": "Welcome to 168 Rowayton Ave, a historic in-town duplex located in the seaside village of Rowayton, CT. This charming 1800 colonial features three bedrooms, three full baths, and original hardwood floors that add to its timeless appeal. The home offers sun-filled rooms with picturesque water views of the 5 Mile River and Pinkney Park.  Recent renovations include a modern kitchen and a stylish primary bathroom, seamlessly blending historic charm with contemporary amenities. Enjoy the best of both worlds in this unique property that captures the essence of Rowayton&apos;s vibrant community. Don&apos;t miss the incredibly charming additional room down stairs and the private backyard sanctuary. This home provides a perfect balance of historic character and modern convenience, inviting you to experience all that Rowayton has to offer, just in time for summer!",
